data.description: Welcome to your 2 story home conveniently located with easy access to the VA Medical Center and just a short commute for military families! Offering a perfect blend of modern & comfortable living, 4 spacious bedrooms & a versatile loft space, this home design will meet the needs of many lifestyles. Step inside to an inviting foyer that leads to an open-concept living area. The living room is warm & welcoming, & the adjacent dining area seamlessly connects to a modern kitchen with quartz countertops. The primary bedroom is a tranquil retreat with a walk-in closet and an ensuite bathroom featuring a tub & separate shower. The loft space on the second floor serves as a versatile area, perfect for a home theater, playroom, or an additional lounge space. The backyard provides an oasis with a patio & great lighting ideal for outdoor dining & entertaining. The low-maintenance landscaping ensures you can enjoy beautiful Las Vegas weather without spending excessive time on yard work.
